<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="563" type="notes">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="563">Notes.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="563">
<bibRefCitation author="Morita, S" journalOrPublisher="Elytra" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" pagination="21 - 26" refId="B32" refString="Morita, S, 2009a. Notes on the Bembidiinae (Coleoptera, Carabidae) of Japan. XVIII. Two New Species of the Genus Bembidion from Southwest Japan. Elytra 37: 21 - 26" title="Notes on the Bembidiinae (Coleoptera, Carabidae) of Japan. XVIII. Two New Species of the Genus Bembidion from Southwest Japan." volume="37" year="2009 a">Morita (2009a)</bibRefCitation>
described 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Neri &amp; Toledano" authorityYear="2021" baseAuthorityName="Neri &amp; Toledano" baseAuthorityYear="2009" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion yoshidai" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="yoshidai">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">Bembidion yoshidai</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from SW Japan and in a note reported that the species is closely related to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Netolitzky" authorityYear="1939" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion trajectum" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="trajectum">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">Bembidion trajectum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Netolitzky, 1939 (currently listed as 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Muller-Motzfeld" authorityYear="1998" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Politophanes" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Politophanes" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">Politophanes</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
); slightly later, Morita himself (2009b) followed 
<bibRefCitation author="Toledano, L" editor="Toledano, L" journalOrPublisher="Sezione Scienze della Vita" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" pagination="5 - 46" publicationUrl="http://www.museostorianaturaleverona.it/media/_Musei/_StoriaNaturale/_Allegati/Biblioteca/Altre%20pubblicazioni/Pubblicazioni%20collaboratori/Toledano/2008_Systematic_notes_Palaearctic_Bembidion_Latrelle.pdf" refId="B54" refString="Toledano, L, 2008. Systematic notes on the Palaearctic Bembidion Latreille, 1802 (Coleoptera, Carabidae) with particular reference to the fauna of China. In: Toledano, L, Ed., Contributions to the knowledge of the eastern Palaearctic Bembidiina (Insecta, Coleoptera, Carabidae). Memorie del Museo Civico di Storia Naturale di Verona 2. Serie. Sezione Scienze della Vita 18: 5 - 46, http://www.museostorianaturaleverona.it/media/_Musei/_StoriaNaturale/_Allegati/Biblioteca/Altre%20pubblicazioni/Pubblicazioni%20collaboratori/Toledano/2008_Systematic_notes_Palaearctic_Bembidion_Latrelle.pdf" title="Systematic notes on the Palaearctic Bembidion Latreille, 1802 (Coleoptera, Carabidae) with particular reference to the fauna of China." url="http://www.museostorianaturaleverona.it/media/_Musei/_StoriaNaturale/_Allegati/Biblioteca/Altre%20pubblicazioni/Pubblicazioni%20collaboratori/Toledano/2008_Systematic_notes_Palaearctic_Bembidion_Latrelle.pdf" volume="18" volumeTitle="Contributions to the knowledge of the eastern Palaearctic Bembidiina (Insecta, Coleoptera, Carabidae). Memorie del Museo Civico di Storia Naturale di Verona 2. Serie." year="2008">Toledano (2008</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Toledano, L" journalOrPublisher="Acta Entomologica Musei Nationalis Pragae" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" pagination="577 - 598" publicationUrl="https://www.aemnp.eu/data/article-1247/1228-49_2_577.pdf" refId="B55" refString="Toledano, L, 2009. Notes on the Bembidiina of Taiwan with description of three new species (Coleoptera: Carabidae). Acta Entomologica Musei Nationalis Pragae 49: 577 - 598, https://www.aemnp.eu/data/article-1247/1228-49_2_577.pdf" title="Notes on the Bembidiina of Taiwan with description of three new species (Coleoptera: Carabidae)." url="https://www.aemnp.eu/data/article-1247/1228-49_2_577.pdf" volume="49" year="2009">2009</bibRefCitation>
) and assigned the species to the subgenus 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion (Ocydromus)" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subGenus" subGenus="Ocydromus">Bembidion Ocydromus</taxonomicName>
Clairville, 1806 s. l. Based on the aedeagal characters reported by 
<normalizedToken originalValue="MÃ¼ller-Morzfeld">Mueller-Morzfeld</normalizedToken>
(1998) and 
<bibRefCitation author="Schmidt, J" journalOrPublisher="Entomologische Blaetter und Coleoptera," pageId="0" pageNumber="563" pagination="361 - 406" refId="B50" refString="Schmidt, J, 2018. Alpha taxonomy from the Himalaya-Tibet orogen: New species and new synonymies in Bembidion Latreille, and a new key to species of the subgenus Bembidionetolitzkya Strand (Coleoptera, Carabidae, Bembidiini). Entomologische Blaetter und Coleoptera, 114: 361 - 406" title="Alpha taxonomy from the Himalaya-Tibet orogen: New species and new synonymies in Bembidion Latreille, and a new key to species of the subgenus Bembidionetolitzkya Strand (Coleoptera, Carabidae, Bembidiini)." volume="114" year="2018">Schmidt (2018)</bibRefCitation>
, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Neri &amp; Toledano" authorityYear="2021" baseAuthorityName="Neri &amp; Toledano" baseAuthorityYear="2009" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion yoshidai" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="yoshidai">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">Bembidion yoshidai</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
must also be transferred to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Muller-Motzfeld" authorityYear="1998" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Politophanes" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Politophanes" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">Politophanes</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
